@NODE "Usage"

       To start ChaoZGui, doubleklick it ..
       @{b}@{u}IMPORTANT!!@{uu}@{ub} - @{b}DONT@{ub} trash the ICON .. ..
       ChaoZGui uses the TOOLTYPES on it :)..


       @{b}Play@{ub} -  Plays the MP file.

       @{b}Load@{ub} -  Loads an MP file .

       @{b}About@{ub}-  @{"About" link Copyright} ChaoZGui ... :)

       @{b}Convert@{ub} @{"Convert" link Convert} Conver Options...

       @{b}Exit@{ub} -  Quit the whole program :(.

       @{b}Prefs@{ub}-  @{"Preferences.." link Preferences}

       You can iconify ChaoZgui by pressing the @{b}CLOSE@{ub} gadget
       on the main window...

@ENDNODE

