@NODE "Install"

       Just move the @{b}ChaoZGui@{ub} drawer wherever you want,
       then configure the Preferences in the program.. :)...

       @{b}Remember@{ub} that all the files of ChaoZGui must be in the
       same directory ;)... Or strange things may happen(!)...

       You will also need to install Mpega.. Somwhere on your HD :)..
       @{b}FILENAME: MPEGA@{ub}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "intro"

       It all began when a IRC friend .. upped me MPEGA 2.2 :)
       MPEGA is developed by @{b}Stephane Tavenard@{ub}, and is a
       extremly fast MP player.. MP1-MP3  :)...
       When i got it . . i liked it .. (ofcourse :)....
       But there was something missing!!.. A GUI!! :)..
       So .. I took it into my own hands .. and made a gui for
       this wonderfull utility!..
       @{b}@{u}And here it is!!@{uu}@{ub}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "reqs"

       -An Amiga. (Not again! :)

       -MPEGA 3.1+ (recommended!)

       -OS2+

       -HD Recommended (are there still souls without HDs?!)

@ENDNODE

