@NODE "Important"

        If you have a CFG file ChaoZgui may not be able to find your
        @{b}MPEGA.CFG@{ub} in worst cases. If not... @{u}disable it@{uu} yourself,
        or ChaoZgui may act strangely!

        The @{b}MPEGA.CFG@{ub} file is looked for in:

        PROGDIR:
        C:
        ENV:
        ENVARC:
        S:
        MPEGA LOCATION: (Set in ChaoZGui Prefs.)

@ENDNODE
